                "text": "What’s included: Admission The Legacy of a Generation Show"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "How to use: Show Mobile Ticket: at Encore Melaka's Box Office counter"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Present your voucher and exchange it for a physical ticket at Encore Melaka's Box Office counter. Kindly refer here to view the seating plan. Seats are decided by the system on a first come first served basis. Customers who purchase tickets of the same price at the same time will be seated together. Outside food and drinks are not allowed inside the venue. Dangerous materials and items such as bottles, firecrackers, lasers, and other things that may disturb or inconvenience other attendees are prohibited inside the venue. Smoking and drinking is not allowed. You will immediately be asked to leave if caught by a staff member."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
